column13:
Instructions:
1. Pick a side on which you'll paddle on.
2. Put your name and last name in their corresponding spots. 
3. Come to practice on time and have fun.

Some important notes:
★ Please make sure to sign-up at least 24 hours before practice.
★ Try your best to arrive on time.
★ Can’t come anymore? Let an exec know if you won't be able to make it anymore. (See table below for the contact information of each exec).
★ For more information, read our info doc: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fKapNs7eq-nNn2XtlhSWeXAmX5i6pcTfqyWxwSshaRs/edit?usp=sharing
